Applications are now being accepted from organizations that wish to sign up as an exhibitor for the NSBE 43rd Annual Convention, to be held March 29-April 2, in Kansas City, Mo. Your competitors will be there… Will you?</p>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\tWith over 10,000 enthusiastic and motivated students and professionals in attendance, #NSBE43 gives your organization the unique opportunity to recruit talent from diverse backgrounds, experience levels and engineering disciplines.</p>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\tWhether you’re looking for students, interns, recent graduates or experienced engineers, you’ll find them at the NSBE Career Fair.
